downloadTitle: MVP Session 23: Import and Use CAD Drawings in Visio 2010 (working file)
downloadDescription: Practice importing and working with computer-aided design (CAD) drawings in Microsoft Visio 2010 with this diagram, part of the Visio 2010 MVP Sessions, Video 23.
detailsSection: Practice importing and working with CAD drawings in Visio 2010 with this diagram, created as a companion to the Visio 2010 MVP Sessions, Video 23 (http://visio.microsoft.com/MVPSessions). MVP Sessions Video 23 covers how you can import, edit, and work with CAD drawings in Visio 2010. Use this diagram to follow along with the video and practice adding overlay assets, connecting them to data sources, and using layers to show only the important elements.
installInstructionSection: Click Download to save the working file to your computer and then open the diagram with Visio 2010.
additionalInformationSection: Watch the Import and Use CAD Drawings video (http://visio.microsoft.com/en-us/Get_Started/How_To/Pages/Session-23-Import-and-use-CAD-drawings.aspx).
